com.rscja.deviceapi

Class RFIDWithISO14443B

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.deviceapi.RFIDWithISO14443B

  • public class RFIDWithISO14443B
extends java.lang.Object
    RFID模块ISO14443B协议操作类
    RFID module ISO14443B protocol operation type

    注意：
    Attention:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Make sure this module is installed before using.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directoy \libs\armeabi\ then module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 free() 关闭设备
    3. call init() to switch on the device before operating, call free() to switch off the device after using.

    Author:
    liuruifeng
